### Backend — AI Service Layer

#### [NEW] `backend/src/ai/services/rfpCopilotService.js`

The orchestration engine. Contains 3 core methods:

| Method | Purpose | Anti-Hallucination Layers Used |
|---|---|---|
| `extractRequirements(tenderId)` | Calls LLM to parse tender text into structured requirement objects | Schema Forcing, Confidence Scoring |
| `generateSection(sectionType, context)` | Generates one proposal section with grounded context | Schema Forcing, RAG Grounding, Confidence Scoring |
| `validateSection(section, requirements)` | Runs fact-check verification pass against tender requirements | Fact Verification, Compliance Audit |

#### [NEW] `backend/src/ai/schemas/rfpSchemas.js`

Zod validation schemas for every LLM output shape. If the LLM returns invalid JSON, the schema error message is fed back into a retry prompt.

#### [NEW] `backend/src/ai/prompts/rfpPrompts.js`

Versioned prompt templates with:
- System prompts establishing domain expertise and output constraints
- Few-shot examples for each section type
- Explicit "DO NOT fabricate" guardrails
- `COMPANY_CONTEXT` and `TENDER_CONTEXT` injection slots

